Package: BiocNMF
Type: Package
Title: Fast Non-negative Matrix Factorization for Single Cell and Spatial Data
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2025-09-09
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Totty", email = "mictott@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: This package provides high-performance non-negative matrix 
    factorization (NMF) methods for SingleCellExperiment and SpatialExperiment 
    objects using the RcppML backend. It enables efficient dimensionality 
    reduction, feature extraction, and pattern discovery in single-cell and 
    spatial genomics data, with seamless integration into Bioconductor workflows.
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.3.0),
    BiocGenerics,
    SingleCellExperiment
Imports:
    methods,
    stats,
    utils,
    S4Vectors,
    SummarizedExperiment,
    RcppML,
    parallel,
    Matrix
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
